title: 10/08/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick show, DP talks to Ross Tucker about some of his takeaways from last night's Rams/Seahawks games. Bill Plaschke calls in to discuss the MLB Playoffs and how he thinks the Giants/Dodgers Series ends up. Plus, Brady Quinn explains what this University of Georgia Football team reminds him of.
